text: Mikaella Chaliou (born 27 August 1991) is a Cypriot footballer who plays as a forward for First Division club Lefkothea Latsion and the Cyprus women's national team. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Cypriot women's footballers Category:Cyprus women's international footballers
